# .helix/

State directory for [helixcli](https://github.com/automanfromm87/helix).
**Don't edit by hand** — generators read and rewrite this on every call.

## Files

- `manifest.json` — authoritative project map. Lists routes, endpoints,
  models that helixcli knows about. The agent (and the Helix backend)
  reads this to seed planning context.
- `README.md` — this file.

## Stack

- Frontend: `{{ manifest.stack.frontend or "(none)" }}`
- Backend: `{{ manifest.stack.backend or "(none)" }}`
- Database: `{{ manifest.stack.database or "(none)" }}`

## Commands available

```
helixcli page <Name>                          add a frontend page
helixcli endpoint <METHOD> <path>             add a backend endpoint
helixcli migration <name>                     alembic revision wrapper
```
